# Learning log lives here.
#
# Append-only record of every learning interaction.
#
# File naming: YYYY-MM-DD-<session-slug>.md
# Schema:
#
# ---
# session_id: <uuid>
# started_at: <ISO-8601>
# ended_at: <ISO-8601>
# domain: <domain-slug>
# concepts_touched: [<concept_id>, ...]
# format: dialogue | quiz | reading | podcast-review | synthesis
# mode: socratic | didactic | exploratory
# outcome: advanced | reinforced | stuck | abandoned
# signals:
#   avg_response_ms: <int>
#   hesitation_events: <int>
#   corrections_asked: <int>
#   follow_up_questions: <int>
#   self-reported-mood: 1-5
# ---
#
# Full transcript or summary below.
#
# This log is the source of truth for assess-progress and adapt-style skills.
